@Node features "Features"
@{B}Features@{UB}

EpicES has the following features:

* User-definable viewers for text, images, samples, animations and modules.

* Pre-definable saves directory (for text only at this stage).

* All subjects matching search criteria are displayed and selectable from
  a standard listview.

* Subject text displayed in the interface via listview.

* World-info text is treated the same way as all the other subjects.

* "People-MESS" archive searchable whilst in LhA form!

* User-setable Index file locations.

@EndNode

