@Node history "History"
@{B}History@{UB}

V1.02 -	Added infotext listview. Viewers support. States when searching
	begins and ends.

V1.03 -	Gadgets expand/move to accomadate window size.

V1.04 -	Added "Interact" button. Changed gadget layout. Seperated viewer
	strings.
	Fixed Gadget refresh after window resize problems.
	States number of subject entries found.
	Now only finds animation without sound.

V1.05 -	Added menus:- About, Quit, Copy text, Index files, Viewers, save
	settings.
	Implemented About requester and quit menu item.
	Index files prefs window added. All functioning.

V1.06 -	Visual Prefs support added to main window.
	Save Settings routine implemented.
	Added "Font" menu item.
	8x8 font can now be loaded for the GUI and menus. Font saves.

V1.07 -	Implemented WorldInfo search and view with textwrap.
	Fixed error upon failing to read index files.
	Merged hdindex search with cdindex search.
	"Save Text" menu item saves to pre-defined directory.
	"Viewers" menuitem changed to "Save Path".
	"Save Path" now works.

V1.08 -	Added "Viewers" settings window - fully functional for all 5 viewers.
	Added viewers to save list.
	WorldInfo Directory selector added to Index files prefs window.
	Index files prefs window functionality now same as that of viewers
	prefs; String gadget reflects new setting after "OK" is pressed in 
	the file requester, and string gadget may be used to alter the file
	path.
	Added version string to about requester.

V1.09 -	Implemented "People-MESS" search. Using "Lha vq" to list the
	found items, and "Lha e" to extract the subject"s infotext.
	Added "Use People-Mess" and " Use WoldInfo" menu items so that
	searching of these can be de-activated for speed.
	Added LhA to "Viewers" and "People-MESS" archive location to Index
	files prefs. Uploaded (05/10/02).

@EndNode
